Some trade secrets should never be unveiled lest the show should lose its special mystique. Taylor's ability to perform even with a broken heart serves as a clear testament of her complete professional dedication to her fans and unparalleled musical career. Ironically, the last thing a true fan would ever want to see is their favorite artist wallowing in deep emotional pain while millions of people sigh at her every move. May she really find a special someone who stays be her side even when the going gets tough. For a unique artist so loved by millions of fans to feel underappreciated by her own lover is a tragedy sincerely worth avoiding, especially if the show must go on. As Freddie Mercury once sang, "Inside my heart is breaking, my makeup may be flaking, but my smile still stays on."
